oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Restaurant at the Glass House Motel
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Restaurant at the Glass House Motel. There is also a gas station in front of the motel.
It was one of the early motels with tourist cabins and a restaurant in Scott County. It was on Highway 27 between Helenwood and New River.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Looking Back at Tennessee Photograph Collection, 1890-1981
